    "The essence of this approach was further crystallized with the publication of the \"China STEM Education White Paper\" by the \"Chinese Academy of Educational Sciences\" in June 2017 and the launch of the \"China STEM Education 2029 Innovation Action Plan\" in May 2018 (Aziz and Rowland, 2018; Quan, 2020).",
    "These actions collectively marked the official commencement of comprehensive reforms in STEM education and curricula in China, fostering the gradual integration of STEM concepts into broader curriculum standards and facilitating the development of teachers' adherence to STEM pedagogies (Lyu et al. 2022).",
